Hnws_list:Lists all Subject lines in a LoF window.|MOnly useful if the file contain multiple articles.
Hnws_next:Select moves caret to next Subject line|MAdjust moves caret to previous Subject line.
Hnws_join:Wraps the current paragraph or the selected text.
Hnws_splt:Unwraps the current paragraph or the selected text.
Hnws_snd:Formats the selected text to 70 chars, saves it and kills the window.
Hnws_snp:Select replaces the selected block with: [snip].|mAdjust replaces the selected with an empty line.
Hnws_sig:Select will remove a quoted sig.|MAdjust will replace quoted sig with sig file.|MCtrl-Select will remove normal sig.|MCtrl-Adjust will replace normal sig with sig file.
Hnws_tidy:Replace top-bit set characters and control codes by a space.

Group2:Main header lines
Group3:Other header lines
Group4:URLs
Group5:Quote >
Group6:Quote >>
Group7:Quote >>>
Group8:Quote >>>>
